                <note rend="inline" type="source">811.20261/49: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of State</gloss> to
                        the Chargé in Denmark</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Grant-Smith</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1919-05-27T12:00:00-04:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">May 27, 1919, noon</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>1637. Your 3984, 15th. Department has positive report from American Consul,
                    Vladivostok, confirmed by <persName corresp="#p_GMGWS1">General
                        Graves</persName>, that Americans have not taken any Bolshevik prisoners in
                    Siberia either at Blagovestchensk or elsewhere.</p>
                <p>What can be done to release Kalamatiano?</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <persName corresp="#p_PFL">
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Polk</hi>
                        </persName>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
